WEBVTT

00:01:33.166 --> 00:01:34.167
Pito: LLENN.

00:01:34.234 --> 00:01:36.969
‐ What is it, Pito?

00:01:37.037 --> 00:01:41.374
‐ I'm so happy you decided
to participate in S.J. 2.

00:01:41.441 --> 00:01:44.477
I can't imagine anyone else
pushing me as far as you did.

00:01:44.544 --> 00:01:48.581
Thanks to you, I had the kind
of fight I've been dreaming of.

00:01:48.648 --> 00:01:51.618
‐ Thanks to you,
all I got was a stomachache

