of letting you take third.

00:02:03.963 --> 00:02:06.899
‐ Thanks, but, no, thanks.

00:02:06.966 --> 00:02:10.603
I can't settle for anything less
than number one.

00:02:10.670 --> 00:02:11.938
Don't get me wrong.

00:02:12.005 --> 00:02:13.906
