that matters to me.

00:02:13.973 --> 00:02:18.178
It never did. All I want is
to survive this battle royale...

00:02:19.279 --> 00:02:20.613
and I intend to.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.515
‐ But it's just a game.

00:02:22.582 --> 00:02:24.284
